o Shrines: A Guide to the Sacred Sites of Japan's Ancient Religion|last1=Cali|first1=Joseph|last2=Dougill|first2=John|last3=Ciotti|first3=Geoff|date=2013|publisher=University of Hawai'i Press|isbn=9780824837136}}</ref>||[[Ichinomiya]]||[http://21coe.kokugakuin.ac.jp/db/jinja/490101.html] |- |colspan=8 style="background-color:#ccffcc;"|'''[[Aki District, Hiroshima|Aki]]''' 1座（大） |- |'''多家神社'''||ohoiheno||Myojin Taisha<ref name=":3" />|| ||[[Take Shrine]]||[[Fuchū, Hiroshima (town)|Fuchu]], [[Aki District, Hiroshima]]||[[Sōja shrine]]<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":0" />||[http://21coe.kokugakuin.ac.jp/db/jinja/490301.html] |}
