There are three such listed shrines. All three of these shrines are Myojin Taisha.<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=https://aki-fuchu.jp/english/introduction_e_right.htm|access-date=2023-12-02|website=aki-fuchu.jp}}</ref><ref name=":4" /> These are called the "Three Great Shrines of [[Aki Province]]" and include [[Hayatani Shrine]], [[Itsukushima Shrine]] and [[Take Shrine]].<ref name=":4">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LPq-lhGqzgEC&q=Hayatani+Shrine|title=Hiroshima|date=1986|publisher=Hiroshima City|language=en}}</ref>
